This is a native bare-swift package; it is not derived from any upstream
Rust crate. The civil-date conversion algorithms (`daysFromCivil`,
`civilFromDays`) are derived from Howard Hinnant's "date_algorithms"
public-domain reference (http://howardhinnant.github.io/date_algorithms.html).
The Sakamoto weekday-of-date algorithm (used in `RFC1123.serialize`) is
similarly public-domain.

RFC 3339: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc3339.html
RFC 1123: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc1123.html
RFC 7231 (IMF-fixdate): https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc7231.html
